    "gp_section_558719091800671336": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091800671336",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "d2551739000a932fb0cf4094a93843af03ffd6d933e6f742e1be727be9727feb_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>You Are Just 15-Minutes Away From Being FREE of Stabbing Back Pain</strong></span>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "If You Want To Relieve Sciatica And Back Pain… You Must Start With Your Spinal Discs",
        "ggN5O792d2I_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggN5O792d2I_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN5O792d2I_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/560e1b00e09a4822b3dd9099f72c91b8.mp4",
        "ggN5O792d2I_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cb6ab29a-5399-4688-b30b-bbc4cecace4c.png",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "If You Want To Relieve Sciatica And Back Pain… You Must Start With Your Spinal Discs",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Your spinal discs act as the shock absorbers between your vertebrae, cushioning your spine and protecting your nerves.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>When at full height, you should be able to move and bend without any issues, and your discs should be able to absorb any impact with ease.</p>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>But imagine, as we sit for prolonged periods, work long hours, and grow older…</p>",
        "ggRTR9XYKM9_text": "<p>Our discs dry out and shrink, forcing the vertebrae closer together and putting pressure on the nerves.</p>",
        "ggWaLe4w3DQ_text": "<p>This is the root cause of Sciatica and the leading reason why back pain and stiffness feel never ending.</p>",
        "gg0045cZav__text": "<p>And until you rehydrate your spinal discs, the pain will never truly go away.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_558719091801523304": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091801523304",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "1f3f270642c90c7c5155998f4040287a5478b8f3ae8d11cf75d6477a1c5eae48_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager Restores Spinal Disc Hydration and Relieves Pressure on Your Sciatic Nerve",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/d6b555b3f24e4fd2b87985bb36f0c056.mp4",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0209d18f-e6fa-4597-b98d-4436aad315a8.png",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager Restores Spinal Disc Hydration and Relieves Pressure on Your Sciatic Nerve",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>The <strong>SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager</strong> fully harnesses the power of three advanced therapies to relieve nerve compression, stiffness, and pain in your back and legs.</p>",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>The moment you lay back on the <strong>SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager</strong>, you'll immediately feel the powerful combination of <strong>dynamic traction, target point massage, and soothing heat therapy</strong> working together.</p>",
        "ggu6Yd3u6Yx_text": "<p><strong>Dynamic Traction:</strong> Gently stretches and separates your vertebrae, reducing nerve compression and creating space for discs to rehydrate.</p>",
        "ggyZ6Gf5lWo_text": "<p><strong>Target Point Massage:</strong> Targets tight muscles and deep knots, easing tension and improving circulation for faster relief.</p>",
        "ggrYT7cGWvp_text": "<p><strong>Soothing Heat Therapy: </strong>Warms tissues and enhances fluid absorption, accelerating disc rehydration and healing.</p>",
        "ggjZnI4Pmdn_text": "<p>These three therapies work in perfect harmony to rehydrate your discs and bring lasting relief.</p>",
        "gg_-bnIX9QK_text": "<p>The best part?</p>",
        "gglNkdnoYHM_text": "<p>You can use it from the comfort of your own home, even in your bed.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_558719091800802408": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091800802408",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "dc2265e8821aae34f24375cd4dc9e565b2b2e21f16059801137b66ff8e63a92f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Recommended",
        "ggr9awOTvod_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggr9awOTvod_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggr9awOTvod_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0c82734003f546349dd4f4973892f5d3.mp4",
        "ggr9awOTvod_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2a6a94d0-4336-4d76-b84e-87225ce357b8.png",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Recommended",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>Physical therapists and spine specialists aren't always within reach and can be very expensive. </p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine \"Triple Fusion\" Massager has been designed alongside leading spine specialists as an effective way to get relief from back pain and Sciatica.</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p>For less than 1/3 of the cost of a single therapy session, you can get results that last a lifetime.</p>",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "The Perfect Therapy Every Time",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/b7221154784149ef88a1a4ed183ca2bf.mp4",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f4168f84-60f8-43e4-a2ce-1927cf520f17.png",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "The Perfect Therapy Every Time ",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p><strong>The Entire Country Is Raving About the SmoothSpine™ \"Triple Fusion\" Massager!</strong></p>",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>Users are reporting significant improvements after just a few sessions! And almost everyone continues using it daily.</p>",
        "ggaFHF5sugD_text": "<p>This means that within a few days of using the<strong> SmoothSpine™ \"Triple Fusion\" Massager</strong>, you can expect to start noticing:</p>",
        "gg3GwCpV-GT_text": "<p><strong>Freedom from discomfort in your back and legs </strong></p>",
        "gg0znNmAU8T_text": "<p><strong>Improved mobility and less pain</strong></p>",
        "ggOLny2Lf9H_text": "<p><strong>Better nights of sleep feeling more rested</strong></p>",
        "ggSvIZrM2QP_text": "<p><strong>Boosted confidence while walking and standing</strong></p>",
        "ggYhZQDCRPW_text": "<p>In just 15 minutes a day, you can give yourself another shot at a normal, comfortable life.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_558719091801064552": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091801064552",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "a773e26446d5ed2b31f8ca8923e3d7ea6ff704b8302e3b6d6d11ae8ea4fc7449_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "How SmoothSpine “Triple Fusion” Massager Works",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/4b62cf66768542578f49af24488d3063.mp4",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f94563b9-6efc-4975-b606-a597a008cc19.png",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "How SmoothSpine “Triple Fusion” Massager Works",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>The best part about the SmoothSpine™ Massager is that it’s <strong>so simple to use.</strong></p>",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p>First, <strong>no short-lived batteries </strong>- You just plug it in using the cable that arrives together with your order.</p>",
        "ggLpXZltW4C_text": "<p>The second step is to <strong>position SmoothSpine under your lower back</strong> and then use the button controls to start the program of traction, heat, and massage. <strong>Lay back and relax while SmoothSpine does its magic.</strong></p>",
        "ggd9w5iVAlN_text": "<p>With consistent use, the <strong>damage to your spine can be reversed</strong>, providing long-lasting relief and allowing you to get back to living your life to the fullest without being held back by back pain or Sciatica.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_558719091801130088": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091801130088",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "54522835b6e8b09e8a6ba07790dac1fde2a5c92961d91224ea5866163942a2c3_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggNH0yZYdL0_text": "Try It for 90 Days, 100% Risk-Free",
        "ggr-cdETAvt_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f56efdea-c394-4196-8c2d-0c85230a19dc.png",
        "ggDerpXpkv1_text": "Try It For 90 Days, 100% Risk-Free",
        "ggNmha1SiOD_text": "<p>Here’s the deal: We believe in this product so much that <strong>we don’t want you to spend a dime until you are 100% certain that it works for you.</strong></p>",
        "ggCn6xOSitZ_text": "<p>That’s why we are offering a <strong>90-day “Results or Refund” guarantee.</strong></p>",
        "gg1rlZNSakA_text": "<p>Simply get yourself a <strong>SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager</strong> today, use it for 90 days, and then make your decision based on the results. <strong>If you are not absolutely thrilled with the relief, we will issue you an immediate refund.</strong></p>",
        "ggGwm1Shj_V_text": "<p>In other words, you are only paying if it <strong>truly works</strong> and helps you reclaim a pain-free life.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_558719091801457768": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091801457768",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "3a1d28238c6832a984b76950c235626a9a6ff4a4c6e49ec845df42250796ccd6_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggchiUpfJH2_text": "The SmoothSpine Massager Is The Safer, Healthier Choice",
        "ggZWYjcI0Sj_text": "<p>It’s non-addictive, works fast, and actually does GOOD things for your body.</p>",
        "gg6YHdZykSx_text": "SmoothSpine Massager",
        "gg_uUJJZYot_text": "<p>DRUG-FREE PAIN RELIEF</p>",
        "ggnUORZ6q9u_text": "<p>It’s natural and non-habit-forming.</p>",
        "ggGTEluwLZX_text": "<p>FAST-ACTING &amp; EFFECTIVE</p>",
        "ggd0hjAxMgS_text": "<p>Works in as little as 15 minutes!</p>",
        "ggcIYxRgigt_text": "<p>BACKED BY EXPERTS</p>",
        "ggcFzCiQ6WE_text": "<p>\"Highly recommended to anyone dealing with Sciatica, herniated discs, and back pain.\"</p>",
        "ggOZidTxPrt_text": "<p>LONG-LASTING RELIEF</p>",
        "ggopNT52XXD_text": "<p>Daily use can even completely realign your spine and rehydrate your discs.</p>",
        "ggcBzCOcsVE_text": "<p>EASY TO USE AT HOME</p>",
        "ggQzsqtEZek_text": "<p>No need for expensive doctor visits.</p>",
        "gg1l9ZsD4ZL_text": "Other Pain Relief Methods",
        "ggFlaRsfX_r_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggabMzZulc1_text": "<p>RELY ON DRUGS &amp; CHEMICALS</p>",
        "gg35L5tHWLl_text": "<p>Which can cause side effects and addiction.</p>",
        "ggplNJpBZcA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggU6Cofrkcy_text": "<p>TAKE HOURS TO WORK</p>",
        "ggiY6BubJDN_text": "<p>Painkillers and other methods take hours or even days to show results.</p>",
        "gggZo7nOlQf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggS6aIr0DXf_text": "<p>QUESTIONED BY DOCTORS</p>",
        "gg8B9W6Nh6g_text": "<p>Medical professionals are increasingly skeptical of long-term painkiller use.</p>",
        "ggAE6F26brb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "gg1WJODqwGE_text": "<p>SHORT-ACTING, REQUIRES CONSTANT USE</p>",
        "ggqa-TsithJ_text": "<p>Painkillers wear off quickly, forcing you to take more doses.</p>",
        "gg6FUm3nxa8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggun2f_DN31_text": "<p>HARMFUL TO YOUR BODY</p>",
        "ggjhrjWgMyc_text": "<p>Painkillers also don’t help your mood, your stress or your anxiety.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_558719091800540264": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091800540264",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "3d00b61de6885e18d4bf7dc979ac938588b859ebc80f123439bed221dd494088_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggrydDXALPH_text": "Real Users, Real Life-Changing Results",
        "gg_nv0E1WSj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1c86457f-82e8-4596-be87-16d4e2c599b7.png",
        "gg029TQ7PQT_text": "<p>\"Finally, Real Relief After Years of Pain!\"</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>\"I've been struggling with back pain for years, and nothing seemed to work. The first time I used the SmoothSpine Massager, I felt instant relief. After a week, I could sit and stand without that sharp pain shooting down my leg. It’s like my spine finally got the support it needed. I recommended anybody that asked me about it. Thank you again.\"</p>",
        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>Karen M.</p>",
        "ggx_FgcD6ei_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-64cdb672-8481-4658-b56d-0c024a33e7cb.png",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>\"I Can Move Freely Again!\"</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>\"Ok, mine got here last week. I was skeptical at first, but after just a few sessions, my stiffness and sciatica pain improved drastically. I used to dread getting out of bed in the morning because of the pain, but now I can move freely again. So easy to use, and the heat feels amazing on my lower back.\"</p>",
        "ggReBUA1njy_text": "<p>Linda R.</p>",
        "ggcIBXq5yW6_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b0f6786c-b06d-4186-be9c-3b9e1e875fbf.jpg",
        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>\"Didn’t Expect It to Work THIS Well!\"</p>",
        "ggZSVoxxXVa_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(205,223,247);color:rgb(34,35,35);font-size:18px;\">\"I was not expecting this! When I laid down on the smoothspine massager , I could feel my back start to decompress in a good way. The heat and massage combined made a huge difference, and I could actually relax for the first time in months. My wife said I’m walking more upright. Definitely worth it trying!!\"</span></p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>John D.</p>"
      }
    },
