    "gp_section_558719091800605800": {
      "type": "gp-section-558719091800605800",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "1966a061e3fc13a340c116d0956805e706792dd60f59aab8cecfba3e784a347d_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Will SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager Provide Relief From My Sciatica and Back Pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>How Soon Will I Notice Results with SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>What's the Ideal Duration for Each SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager Therapy Session?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Do I need to buy batteries?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>What are the dimensions of the SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Back Massager?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>What is your return policy?</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Absolutely! SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager is your key to relief from Sciatica, back pain, and disc discomfort. Thanks to its innovative \"Triple Fusion\" technology combining dynamic traction, target point massage, and soothing heat therapy.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Get ready for rapid relief! Many users report feeling noticeable improvements after just one session. For long-term relief, regular use is key. SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager ensures continuous comfort and relief by targeting the root cause of back pain.</p>",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>No need to rush - we ‘ve got your comfort covered. A mere 15 minutes a day with SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager is all it takes. It’s like having a personal physical therapist, ready to relieve your back whenever you need it.</p>",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>No, you don’t need to worry about batteries! The SmoothSpine™ Triple Fusion Massager comes with a plug-in power cord, ensuring consistent and uninterrupted therapy without the hassle of recharging or replacing batteries. We recommend using a power source with a minimum of 5V 2A or above for optimal performance.</p>",
        "gguV3bOpKHn_text": "<p>The massager measures <strong>23.6\" (L) × 9.8\" (W) × 4.7\" (H)</strong>. It’s perfectly sized to support your lower back while lying on your bed, couch, or floor—large enough for full coverage, but compact enough to store easily. <i>(For international customers: 60 cm × 25 cm × 12 cm)</i><br><i>Please note: Exact size may vary slightly due to the handcrafted nature of production.</i></p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>If you don’t get the results you want in 90 days or less—we don’t want your money! We are confident that our products work and encourage you to try them risk-free. If you’re not satisfied and wish to return the product, you can do so within our 90-day money-back guarantee. </p>"
      }
    },
